tool_description: Get profile information with proxy image will show directly to your frontend
title: Instagram Profile

api_list.name: GET Video
api_list.description: Get user video with username, use ?next={result.data.page_info.next} for next page
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://instagram-profile1.p.rapidapi.com/getvideo/{username}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "instagram-profile1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
